dc_title_s: Southern Israel structural map on top Judea group
dc_description_s: Geophysical Institute of Israel. Companion text: Appendix C: Top Judea Group - Digital structural map of Israel / Lorian Fleischer and Rina Gafsou. Geological framework of the Levant. Volume I: Cyprus and Syria. Volume II: The Levantine Basin and Israel / John K. Hall; Valey A. Krasheninnikov; Francis Hirsch; Chaim Benjamini; Akiva Flexer. Jerusalem: Historical Productions-Hall. Vol II. 2005. 745-754 p. North Decimal Degree 33.2833. South Decimal Degree 31.4000. East Decimal Degree 35.9500. West Decimal Degree 34.2667.
